_sText:
Here is a T-Rex prefab I made that also roars when you shoot it in the mouth. The download comes with the mp3 file attached to it. Also, you can climb up his tail and get to his head. 

I didn't really find a texture I liked, so I manipulated a prop texture. I wasn't sure I could really make one that went with it well. I didn't like the idea of just a solid green one, though maybe you'll find that that is your preference. 

If anyone uses this in a map, I would love to see their work so please PM me or send a steam friend request to Dr. Kepper
